    "effect": "Cleansing Ritual cleanses one target’s body of poisons or diseases. When activated, the caster makes a Ritual Crafting check against a specific DC to cleanse the target’s body. \nAlcohol and drugs are reasonably easy, with a DC of 12. \nPoisons and oils are harder, with a DC of 15. \nMajor illnesses are very difficult to cleanse, with a DC of 18. \nCleansing Ritual cannot cure plagues such as Catriona.",
